OL,4,CParents react to birth trauma inquiry
OL,6,FThe inquiry was led by the MP for
OL,7,FStafford Theo Clarke, who suffered
OL,8,Fbirth trauma while delivering her
OL,9,Fdaughter, had to undergo a two-hour
OL,10,Fsurgery without general anaesthetic
OL,11,Fafter the birth of her daughter in
OL,12,FAugust 2022.
OL,14,FAnd its findings reflect .JMPs spoke
OL,15,Fto hundreds of parents as part of
OL,16,Ftheir investigation.
