OL,6,FTim and Hannah Taylor-Smith, whose
OL,7,Fbaby boy Zachary died 18 months ago,
OL,8,Fread the results of the inquiry
OL,9,Frevealing poor maternity care for
OL,10,Fthousands of mothers across the
OL,11,Fcountry.
OL,13,FThey said: "It seems the most basic
OL,14,Flevels sometimes is really sub-par.
OL,15,FAnd it seems to be the case across the
OL,16,Fboard as well.
OL,18,F"Through our own experience we've kind
OL,19,Fof learned that it was often the most
OL,20,Fsimplest of things that were forgotten
OL,21,For missed.
