OL,6,F"But obviously since our experience
OL,7,Fwe've spoken to many other families
OL,8,Fwhere that also seems to be the case."
OL,10,FWhat is the Birth Trauma Inquiry and
OL,11,Fwhat has it found?JThe Birth Trauma
OL,12,FInquiry heard evidence from more than
OL,13,F1,300 women who had given birth.
