OL,6,FSome described being left in blood-
OL,7,Fsoaked sheets, while others suffered
OL,8,Flife-changing injuries. Many were also
OL,9,Fmocked, shouted at, and even denied
OL,10,Fbasic pain relief.JShe said: "We've
OL,11,Feven had women who post-natal had
OL,12,Fsevere tears that lead to them having
OL,13,Fbowel incontinence for example."
OL,15,FStafford MP Theo Clarke said: "There
OL,16,Fseems to be a real taboo about taking
OL,17,Fabout risks in childbirth.
