OL,6,F"And I hope by me very publicly
OL,7,Fdiscussing it in my speech in the
OL,8,FChamber, and obviously
OL,9,FParliamentarians stalking about it
OL,10,Ftoday we can try and break that taboo.
OL,12,F"I think what really struck me reading
OL,13,Fthough all of the submissions, and
OL,14,Fevery single one was read and thank
OL,15,Fyou to so many people for writing in,
OL,16,Fis that there does seem to be a
OL,17,Fpostcode lottery in this country in
OL,18,Fmaternity services.
