OL,6,F"And I don't think that's right. And I
OL,7,Fthink the PM needs to do something
OL,8,Fabout it today."
OL,10,FWhat has the birth trauma report
OL,11,Frecommended?JThe report recommends an
OL,12,Foverhaul of maternity and post-natal
OL,13,Fcare in the UK, including recruiting,
OL,14,Ftraining and retaining more midwives &
OL,15,Fobstetricians. Ministers say they are
OL,16,Flistening.JShe says: "We're changing
OL,17,Fthe culture around maternity services,
OL,18,Fmaking it much more focused about mum
OL,19,Fand baby.
