OL,6,FOn Monday, NHS England chief executive
OL,7,FAmanda Pritchard said: "The
OL,8,Fexperiences outlined by women in this
OL,9,Freport are simply not good enough and
OL,10,Fnot what the NHS wants or expects for
OL,11,Fpatients."JShe said the NHS England
OL,12,Fwas working with local health bodies
OL,13,Fto "create and nurture a culture where
OL,14,Fwomen are listened to, their choices
OL,15,Frespected and care is personalised,
OL,16,Fequitable and safe".
