OL,6,FHealth Secretary Victoria Atkins said
OL,7,Fshe was "determined to improve the
OL,8,Fquality and consistency of care for
OL,9,Fwomen throughout pregnancy, birth and
OL,10,Fthe critical months that follow".
OL,12,FIn January, she shared her personal
OL,13,Fexperience of the "darker corners" of
OL,14,Fthe NHS, after giving birth as a
OL,15,Fpatient with type one diabetes.
OL,17,F"I want to reform our NHS and care
OL,18,Fsystem to make it faster, simpler and
OL,19,Ffairer for all of us and that includes
OL,20,Fwomen," she said.
